Physics                   91000
Comp. Sci.           77333.3333
Finance                   85000
Biology                   72000
History                   61000

6 rows selected.
********************************************************************************************
11. Find the departments with the maximum budget.
SQL> select dept_name,budget max_budget
  2  from department
  3  where budget=(select max(budget)
  4  from department);

DEPT_NAME            MAX_BUDGET
-------------------- ----------
Finance                  120000
